text: Winter Carnival is a 1939 American comedy-drama movie directed by Charles Reisner and starring Ann Sheridan, Richard Carlson, Helen Parrish, James Corner, Alan Baldwin, Robert Armstrong, Jimmy Butler, Virginia Gilmore, Joan Leslie. It was distributed by United Artists. == Other websites == * Category:1939 comedy movies Category:1939 drama movies Category:American comedy-drama movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Reisner
